{"tid":782341,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［罪大滔天］Sony公佈Android P更新名單 旗艦裝置預計十一月起可更新","createTime":"2018-08-16T15:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T01:12:11.000Z","uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8ac812d801e7f91f096ff88a8eeee923bbfbd672","tid":782341,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Sony公佈Android P更新名單 旗艦裝置預計十一月起可更新</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thealpha.app/2018/08/sonypie.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thealpha.app%2F2018%2F08%2Fsonypie.html&d=vXIrtQr4zSkx1uc2bfDxF%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=95e34ccf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thealpha.app/2018/08/sonypie.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7aI40tAwEqw/W3Wa-0-byII/AAAAAAAByh0/vpNRZcBLi9MuyCJDkZEgBmc2co9AoAGHQCLcBGAs/s1600/sonypie.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-7aI40tAwEqw%2FW3Wa-0-byII%2FAAAAAAAByh0%2FvpNRZcBLi9MuyCJDkZEgBmc2co9AoAGHQCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fsonypie.png&h=f686f5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSony啱啱公佈咗可以升級Android 9 Pie嘅裝置名單，旗艦裝置預計可以喺今年十一月更新，而中階裝置就預計下年年頭。Sony稱佢哋目標係喺Google發佈咗更新之後盡快為用戶提供更新，亦強調軟件更新要達致佢哋極致標準先會發佈俾用戶。"},{"pid":"9de67dc1d9ca179c6c52ec62c471353859decc19","tid":782341,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"Sony XZ2 Premium<br />\n11.9 mm 厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n236g重&amp;nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n73.2 %Screen To body Ratio&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;<br />\n超粗上下巴&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇3.5mm&amp;nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得64GB選擇，如果用雙卡，好快無位xx<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/235351_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F235351_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6030e385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSmartone都用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee8327becad706558dd93df631b68226c8d2021","tid":782341,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T15:55:30.000Z","msg":"[有片]發現Sony Xperia Xz2嚴重bug<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bkRxBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bkRxBS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n四個月先fix到XZ2呢個bug<br />\n點知XZ2P又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891e8d0781c067f2b3a4fe7d2896ed271ab8af4c","tid":782341,"uid":123177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"fix左舊bug先啦"},{"pid":"055702a024e53d21b0e8c927f9a89398c35f9671","tid":782341,"uid":38426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"sony 汁柒左佢啦"},{"pid":"7d96052b74bd4995e92ebdd23b1705a649ead5f2","tid":782341,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T16:11:32.000Z","msg":"Android P本身已經冇特別，仲要冇得用Overlay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，仲要冇埋Oreo有嘅Quick Setting，真係on9，愈來愈垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，抄iphone用Gesture又要抄唔足，XDA嗰Gesture都好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1aed605da4485dca5a75b9e8c8e